    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "What's your expected output here? `.transform` returns an output with the same shape as the input.\r\n\r\nIt looks like you want `.apply` maybe?\r\n\r\n```python\r\nIn [14]: df.groupby([\"A\"])['B'].apply(mean_of_arrays)\r\n[ 3.  4.  5.  6.]\r\n[ 3.  4.  5.  6.]\r\nOut[14]:\r\nA\r\n1    [3.0, 4.0, 5.0, 6.0]\r\n2    [3.0, 4.0, 5.0, 6.0]\r\nName: B, dtype: object\r\n```"
